body_text:
Can anyone identify this manga? 
I tried looking around Haruhime Scans and didn't turn up with anything that looked promising. I raked my eyes across the whole image to see if the name of the manga was hidden somewhere in the there- it isn't. I did all sorts of google searches I could think of and even tried to pick the guy and girl out of a character database thing but I had no luck. Any ideas?
What manga is this scanlation page from? I see this a lot as one of those scanlation things but I have no idea where this is from.
